Name: Average time from 'SW-Reviewer Agreed' to 'SW-Awaiting EIC Decision'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'SW-Reviewer Agreed' and activity 'SW-Awaiting EIC Decision'

Name: Total time from 'SW-Reviewer Agreed' to 'SW-Awaiting EIC Decision' across all cases
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'SW-Reviewer Agreed' and activity 'SW-Awaiting EIC Decision'

Name: Minimum time from 'SW-Reviewer Agreed' to 'SW-Awaiting EIC Decision'
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'SW-Reviewer Agreed' and activity 'SW-Awaiting EIC Decision'

Name: Average time from 'SW-Awaiting EIC Decision' to 'SW-EIC Major Revision'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'SW-Awaiting EIC Decision' and activity 'SW-EIC Major Revision'

Name: Average time from 'SW-Awaiting EIC Decision' to 'SW-EIC Accept'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'SW-Awaiting EIC Decision' and activity 'SW-EIC Accept'

Name: Total time for 'SW-Awaiting EIC Decision' across all cases
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity SW-Awaiting EIC Decision and the end of the case

Name: Minimum time from 'SW-Awaiting EIC Decision' to 'SW-EIC Reject & Resubmit'
Metric: ERROR: computing metric {'begin': "activity == 'SW-Awaiting EIC Decision'", 'end': "activity == 'SW-EIC Reject & Resubmit'", 'aggregation': 'minimum'}

Name: Average time it takes from 'SW-Awaiting EIC Decision' to the next activity in the process
Metric: The average of the duration between activity SW-Awaiting EIC Decision and the end of the case

Name: Total resolution time of 'SW-Awaiting EIC Decision'
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity SW-Awaiting EIC Decision and the end of the case

Name: Average waiting time to the 'SW-Awaiting EIC Decision' after 'SW-Reviewer Agreed'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'SW-Reviewer Agreed' and activity 'SW-Awaiting EIC Decision'

Name: Time until 'SW-Awaiting EIC Decision' from the start of the process
Metric: The sum of the duration between the start of the case and activity 'SW-Awaiting EIC Decision'

Name: Time from 'SW-Awaiting EIC Decision' to 'SW-EIC Minor Revision'
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'SW-Awaiting EIC Decision' and activity 'SW-EIC Minor Revision'

Name: Time from 'SW-Awaiting EIC Decision' to 'SW-EIC Reject'
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'SW-Awaiting EIC Decision' and activity 'SW-EIC Reject'

Name: Minimum resolution time of 'SW-Awaiting EIC Decision'
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity SW-Awaiting EIC Decision and the end of the case

Name: Total time it takes 'SW-Awaiting EIC Decision' to be done after 'SW-AE Assign Reviewers'
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'SW-AE Assign Reviewers' and activity 'SW-Awaiting EIC Decision'

Name: Average time between 'SW-Awaiting EIC Decision' and 'SW-EIC Major Revision' in the variants where both activities occur
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'SW-Awaiting EIC Decision' and activity 'SW-EIC Major Revision'

Name: Minimum time between 'SW-Awaiting EIC Decision' and any revision decision ('SW-EIC Major Revision', 'SW-EIC Minor Revision', 'SW-EIC Accept', 'SW-EIC Reject & Resubmit')
Metric: ERROR: computing metric {'begin': "activity == 'SW-Awaiting EIC Decision'", 'end': "activity == 'SW-EIC Major Revision' or activity == 'SW-EIC Minor Revision' or activity == 'SW-EIC Accept' or activity == 'SW-EIC Reject & Resubmit'", 'aggregation': 'minimum'}

Name: Average time from 'SW-Awaiting EIC Decision' to 'Manuscript Export Succeeded' in the process variants where a decision leads to a new submission cycle
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'SW-Awaiting EIC Decision' and activity 'Manuscript Export Succeeded'
